            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to add to your collection. While it’s always a gamble trying to determine which cars will soar in value, as time marches on we feel many will realize the true value this car provided as it spearheaded the Cadillac revolution of the 21st century. Finished in a beautiful Blue Steel over Shale leather interior, this car has just 46,548 miles showing. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
